Radha!  - Mohan, apakah kamu...

00:20:02.480 --> 00:20:03.560
Mama.  Radha...

00:20:03.680 --> 00:20:04.680
Radha.  - Radha.

00:20:04.760 --> 00:20:05.840
Radha, buka matamu.

00:20:14.360 --> 00:20:16.320
Radha, bangun.  - Radha.

